Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:05.40,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,840.333)}Hi everyone! I'm Misaki Nako, and I play Arashi Chisato
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.10,0:00:10.20,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,840.333)}Hi hello! I'm Yabushima Akane, and I play Yoneme Mei
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.80,0:00:13.90,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,840.333)}Hi I'm Ookuma Wakana, and I play Wakana Shiki
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:20.10,Shiki,,0,0,0,,So, since today, December 30th, the day this video goes out, is already the end of the year...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:20.10,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,So fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:24.20,Shiki,,0,0,0,,We are doing this as a "take it easy and chat" kind of segment
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.60,0:00:26.20,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,End of the year?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.60,0:00:27.60,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,"End of the year" it said
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.60,0:00:28.90,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,797.667)}It's over tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:35.36,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs40\pos(960,883)}Liella! Roundtable Memo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:35.36,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs40\pos(960,1035)}There's only 1 day left in the year
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.90,0:00:32.40,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}"It ends tomorrow" it said
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:35.00,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}"It ends tomorrow" it said, how do you feel about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.40,0:00:38.60,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,By the way, what's with this gathering today?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:39.80,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you asked!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.80,0:00:40.30,Shiki,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.30,0:00:43.20,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,808.333)}We're gonna keep this pace today, okay? You all good?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.20,0:00:44.30,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,808.333)}Just keep up with me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.30,0:00:50.90,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,728.333)}So us Liella!, about a month for now, January 21, 2026
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:56.20,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,728.333)}We will be releasing the 6th Live Tour Blu-ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:48.03,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs40\pos(960,883)}Liella! Roundtable Memo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:48.03,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs40\pos(960,1035)}This time, we're taking it easy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.03,0:00:56.86,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs40\pos(960,789.667)}Love Live! Superstar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.03,0:00:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs40\pos(960,980.667)}on sale Wed, Jan 21, 2026
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.90,0:01:07.40,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs40\pos(960,789.667)}Love Live! Superstar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.90,0:01:07.40,Ren,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs40\pos(976.667,927)}2026/2/7 (Sat) – 2/8 (Sun) Kanagawa, Yokohama Arena
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.90,0:01:07.40,Ren,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs40\pos(982,985.667)}2026/2/28 (Sat) – 3/1 (Sun) Aichi, Aichi Sky Expo Hall A
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:00:58.60,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,728.333)}And then, just two weeks after that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:00.00,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,728.333)}Two weeks later??
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:03.60,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,728.333)}We'll be holding the 7th Live!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.70,0:01:07.00,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,708.333)}It’s back to back. I can’t believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.30,0:01:13.10,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,701.667)}This time, we're gonna take it easy and look back on our 6th Live moments,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.10,0:01:17.20,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,701.667)}get everyone excited for Blu-ray release,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:22.50,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,701.667)}and then have you come to the 7th Live keeping that same energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.50,0:01:23.40,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,701.667)}The name of the segment is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:23.40,Kinako,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs42\pos(957.333,776.334)}This segment's plan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:23.40,Ren,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs48\pos(960,976.333)}While we {\rWien\fs48}take it easy and look back on our 6th Live Tour memories{\r\fs48},\Nwe will get you excited for the Blu-ray release, and then {\rWien\fs48}come to the 7th Live keeping that same energy!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.56,0:01:37.56,Group - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,757.667)\fnArial\fs55}Liella! 6th Live Tour Blu-ray Release Commemoration!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.30,0:01:29.20,Group - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1035)\fnArial\fs55}From 6th to 7th:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.20,0:01:37.56,Group - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1035)\fnArial\fs55}From 6th to 7th: A Laid-Back Roundtable!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:35.50,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,{\pos(386.667,651)}It really is laid back
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:37.50,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,669.667)}True. We even wearing our tracksuit now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.70,0:01:41.10,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Usually for stuff like this, we wear our school uniform and look all proper
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.10,0:01:42.30,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,Being proper, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:44.00,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,Doesn't mean we're usually improper or anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:45.70,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,How is it? The comfort of it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.70,0:01:46.70,Shiki,,0,0,0,,The comfort?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.70,0:01:49.20,Shiki,,0,0,0,,But I think some people already have these, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:01:52.20,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Maybe there are people watching this in the tracksuit, too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.60,0:01:54.80,Shiki,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I thought we'd be in our uniforms today...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.60,0:01:57.70,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\pos(960,791)}So it's tracksuits, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:02:00.90,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\pos(960,791)}The way you said it, that tone, kinda cracks me up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:02:01.26,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs40\pos(960,883)}Liella! Roundtable Memo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:02:01.26,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs70\pos(960,1029.667)}We are sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:04.10,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Apparently, it's already been half a year since the final show (of 6th)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.30,0:02:05.20,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:07.80,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,But it also feels like it's been longer even
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:12.90,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,We had Revival Live, and day 3 "Connect the Stars" right after
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:16.80,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,So maybe that's why it feels like time flew by even faster
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:21.80,Note with shadow,,0,0,0,,Dassen: off-topic/tangents
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:18.90,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,805.667)}And for this roundtable, some great news!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:20.60,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,805.667)}Going off-topic is totally fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:22.60,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,805.667)}Yay! That's how it is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:23.60,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,735.667)}That's unusual
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:28.00,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,805.667)}We might go off-topic more than usual,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:31.30,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,805.667)}With tangents and all, we hope you stick with us to the end
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.30,0:02:33.30,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,805.667)}Thanks in advance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:35.30,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,805.667)}Please do
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.80,0:02:50.10,Shiki,,0,0,0,,Alright then, let's start with our first segment
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:52.53,Shiki,,0,0,0,,"So, how was the 6th Live Tour?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.53,0:02:56.50,Natsumi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,893.667)\fnArial\fs50}So, how was the 6th Live Tour?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.53,0:02:54.53,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,789.667)}"How was it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:56.53,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,789.667)}Are we calling this a "segment"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:03:07.16,Kinako,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs48\pos(960,824.333)}Segment 1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:03:07.16,Ren,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs48\pos(960,899)}Following the topic we draw from the prompt box
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:03:07.16,Ren,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs48\pos(960,1005.667)}We'll take it easy and looking back on the 6th\NLive Tour as a whole
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:03:00.00,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,735.667)}We all have plenty of memories from the 6th Live Tour, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:04.60,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,735.667)}We'll take it easy and looking back on the live as a whole
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:07.60,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,735.667)}And looks like we've got a prompt box, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:12.60,Shiki,,0,0,0,,And by doing that, we can chat about it too
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:14.10,Shiki,,0,0,0,,Alright then, first up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:16.10,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll draw one
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.10,0:03:18.30,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,We have to remember it first
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:20.00,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,Step one: remembering
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.00,0:03:20.80,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:23.00,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,"What was the tastiest thing we ate?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:26.10,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,The tastiest thing we ate?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:26.10,Shiki,,0,0,0,,The tastiest thing we ate?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:28.10,Shiki,,0,0,0,,Wait, where did we go first?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:29.30,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:29.50,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.30,Shiki,,0,0,0,,I can't remember where we went
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:32.30,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Same
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:33.40,Shiki,,0,0,0,,Fukuoka
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:35.80,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Miyagi... we went there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:37.80,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,We went to Miyagi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:37.80,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,We went to Miyagi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:41.20,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,803)}Uhhh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.30,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,803)}And... that's a wrap
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.30,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs40\pos(957.333,881.666)}Liella! Roundtable Memo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.30,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs70\pos(962.666,984.333)}Miyagi. The End.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:44.30,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,803)}We're done here
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:45.20,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,736.333)}We're so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:48.00,Shiki,,0,0,0,,Miyagi, Fukuoka, Tokyo, Aichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:50.10,Shiki,,0,0,0,,Osaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:50.30,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Osaka was last?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:51.90,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Osaka was the last one
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:52.80,Shiki,,0,0,0,,We didn't go to Aichi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:54.00,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,Was Tokyo first?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:54.80,Shiki,,0,0,0,,We go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:55.90,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,733.667)}"We did," they said
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:04:01.56,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs40\pos(957.333,881.666)}Liella! Roundtable Memo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:04:01.56,Natsumi,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs50\pos(522.666,1002.999)}Correct\NAnswer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:04:01.56,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs55\pos(1050.666,1011)}Tokyo Aichi Miyagi Fukuoka Osaka
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:57.40,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,733.667)}Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:56.30,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,813.667)}We did x 3
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:03:59.90,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,813.667)}But wait, I remember about Osaka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:01.70,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,813.667)}In Osaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:06.00,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,The catering was super fancy every single time
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:10.00,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,Oh you mean the one where they had hot snacks that kept warm, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:12.40,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,It was like a convenience store, like-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:14.80,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,They had pork buns and tons of stuff--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:14.80,Shiki,,0,0,0,,Takoyaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:16.80,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,856.333)}for example... hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:18.80,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,856.333)}Ah! The one where they cooked the takoyaki for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:19.00,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,787)}Yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:19.80,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,856.333)}Was that in 6th?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:20.80,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,856.333)}Yes, during 6th
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:22.60,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,856.333)}Wanaka, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:23.60,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,856.333)}Yeah! It was so good--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.60,0:04:24.50,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,Ah, {\i1}takosen{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.60,0:04:24.50,Note with shadow,,0,0,0,,T/N: Takosen: Osaka street snack where takoyaki\Nis sandwiched in a big crispy shrimp/rice cracker\N(senbei/ebi-sen)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:25.30,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,856.333)}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:27.60,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,856.333)}Everyone was like, "Wakana! Wakana!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:30.90,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,856.333)}The takosen keep sold out, it was so popular
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:35.90,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Almost all the time, it's already gone before you know it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:38.10,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,They prepare a lot of it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:39.50,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Everyone's like "So good! So good!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:42.20,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Then it's gone in no time, and it happens a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:45.90,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,That was my first time ever in my life eating takosen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:50.40,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Never had it at a festival or something? Like a food stall?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:52.30,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,Maybe because I'm from the countryside, we didn't have it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:05:03.13,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs40\pos(957.333,881.666)}Liella! Roundtable Memo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:05:03.13,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs48\pos(901.333,1018.999)}Familiarity in Kanto Area:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:05:03.13,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs48\pos(1234.666,1018.999)}weak
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:53.90,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,813.667)}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:56.00,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,813.667)}Yeah, we don't
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:04:57.40,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,813.667)}Huh, you didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:57.90,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,813.667)}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:04:58.50,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,813.667)}Yeah we don't, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:05:00.00,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,813.667)}Takosen is pretty rare, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:01.50,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,813.667)}Like, that kind of thing is usually...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:01.50,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,736.333)}Yeah, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:03.10,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,813.667)}Not really something you get at the actual venue
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:04.30,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,736.333)}What about {\i1}tamasen{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:13.50,Note with shadow,,0,0,0,,T/N: Tamasen: a Japanese festival snack where\Na fried egg (tamago) plus sauce/toppings like tenkasu\Nare put on or sandwhiched in a large cracker (senbei/ebi-sen).
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:05.50,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tamasen?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:06.40,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,What is arimasen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:07.60,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Huh??
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:29.30,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs36\pos(293.333,821.667)}tamasen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:08.80,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Um, it's like--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:13.50,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Takosen is like, that big cracker with it sandwiched in, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:18.60,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,But tamasen is where they plop a fried egg right on top of the cracker
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:19.10,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,And then sauce--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:20.00,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,So the egg is there-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:20.20,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:22.20,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,With sauce and tenkasu and stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:25.20,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,It's called {\i1}tamasen{\i0}, and it's hard to eat
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:25.20,Note with shadow,,0,0,0,,Nuance: It's messy and quite hard to eat
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:26.40,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Apparently you can't really get it there
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:27.60,Shiki,,0,0,0,,We don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:28.20,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,They don't have it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:29.30,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,Sounds good, though
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:31.80,Shiki,,0,0,0,,Then, what do you have at festivals in your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:37.00,Shiki,,0,0,0,,Like in Nako's Kansai Area you've got takosen and tamasen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:41.33,Note with shadow,,0,0,0,,T/N: Hashimaki ("chopstick roll")
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:38.40,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,There's also {\i1}hashimaki{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:39.90,Shiki,,0,0,0,,What is {\i1}hashimaki{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:41.30,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,Like, it's wrapped around chopsticks
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:41.30,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Let's move on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:42.80,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,What do you two even have, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:43.80,Shiki,,0,0,0,,Wrapped around chopstick?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:45.10,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Wrapped... {\i1}*giggling*{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:47.10,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,It's kinda like okonomiyaki but wrapped
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:48.00,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Not us being wrapped, though
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:50.00,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,Wait, am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:58.16,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs36\pos(293.333,821.667)}Hashimaki
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:50.50,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,No, you're right! You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:52.10,Shiki,,0,0,0,,So it's like "wrapped okonomiyaki"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:53.00,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,It's rolled up like, swirl swirl swirl
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:54.80,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,It's like okonomiyaki, but on a stick
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:56.60,Shiki,,0,0,0,,No, we don't have that in Saitama
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:57.50,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,We don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:06:01.50,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,I honestly thought {\i1}hashimaki{\i0} and {\i1}tamasen{\i0} and {\i1}takosen{\i0} were everywhere in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:02.70,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,so it's surprising to me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:03.50,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:05.50,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,They actually might not be that common
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:08.40,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,You just assume things that you have are "normal"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:10.40,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,They really don't have it at all--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:10.40,Shiki,,0,0,0,,Baby Castella
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:18.03,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs40\pos(957.333,881.666)}Liella! Roundtable Memo
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:18.03,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs70\pos(960,1011)}Baby Castella (nationwide)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:12.10,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}They do have that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:13.50,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}See? Exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:15.50,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}Baby Castella do exist there. Yeah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:16.00,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,701.666)}We have baby castella, okay
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:18.00,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}Sorry. They do, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:20.40,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,How about some sweets and stuff? You like them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:22.40,Shiki,,0,0,0,,Sweets?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:21.80,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Yea
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:26.80,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, eat. Ah-?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:28.80,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:30.30,Shiki,,0,0,0,,Ueehh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:35.03,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs40\pos(957.333,881.666)}Liella! Roundtable Memo
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:35.03,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArialpos(960,974.999)}Ueehh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:33.20,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}What kind of reaction is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:34.80,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}Ueehh... Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:36.80,Shiki,,0,0,0,,For New Year's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:37.10,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:39.00,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,Feels very winter-y
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:42.10,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,This is like, peak winter, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:42.10,Shiki,,0,0,0,,Ah, this, this one
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:44.40,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,This one is good. It melts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:45.30,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,You're gonna say "melty," aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:47.70,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Like, it melts in your mouth like snow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:48.60,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Alright, moving on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:52.50,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,A story that you can only tell now, a {\i1}happening{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:07:06.30,Note with shadow,,0,0,0,,T/N: Happening (ハプニング) a common word used in\NJapanese variety show. It means "incident" or\N"mishap"\N"unexpected moment".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:54.70,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:07:02.73,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs40\pos(957.333,881.666)}Liella! Roundtable Memo
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:07:02.73,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs50\pos(960,1006.999)}Asking-it-like-a-question style
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:57.10,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,704.333)}You asking us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:58.10,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}Because it's "now"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.10,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}"Something that we can say now"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:02.50,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}"Something that we can say now"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.80,0:07:06.30,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,But you know, about this "happening"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:11.90,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,On "Dazzling Game", which we performed on center stage around the middle of the show,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:14.80,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,depending on the venue, there were times when,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:16.50,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,while taking it off...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:25.80,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,I feel like every now and then, I'd take it off too late, or I'd end up leaving the outer attire on the stage
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:28.20,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,But like, no one totally failed to take it off, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:29.60,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Nobody couldn't take it off
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:33.80,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,There were just tiny delays, like a split second
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:37.20,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I still think it's a miracle we managed to pull that off
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:39.30,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,That moment is pretty nerve-wrecking
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:40.00,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Very, very nerve-wracking
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:42.30,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,Like, "I'm definitely taking this off"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:46.00,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Weird thing to say, but in that moment, all I'm thinking about is taking it off
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:51.96,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs40\pos(957.333,881.666)}Liella! Roundtable Memo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:51.96,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1016.333)}Performance < Taking it off
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:47.30,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}Like "Here it comes, here it comes!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:49.30,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}If you only hear this part, it sounds kinda weird
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:51.60,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}Hmm anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:56.30,Shiki,,0,0,0,,You know, sometimes there isn't even time to drink water, but... I saw others drinking a ton too
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:57.20,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Ah, I get that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:07:57.80,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}Right? You get it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:06.13,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs40\pos(957.333,881.666)}Liella! Roundtable Memo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:06.13,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1016.333)\fnArial\fs65}The other members chugging water
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:07:58.70,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,701.666)}You can't see clearly
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:07:59.80,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}You can't see clearly, the name (in each bottles)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:00.20,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:03.20,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}So I’m like, “Whatever, I’ll just drink for now.”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:03.40,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,701.666)}That's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:03.90,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}Yeah. it's better to just drink
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:04.90,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}They were drinking so much
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:07.40,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,And honestly, Shiki-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:12.40,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,you know how you put those name stickers on top of the bottle caps?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:14.30,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Isn't it kind of hard to tell? Like, the colors...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:16.30,Shiki,,0,0,0,,I can't see anything
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:20.00,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,There is like a tiny bit of light on stage when you get a chance to drink water
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:22.00,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,It's lit when you can drink, but
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:26.60,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,with lighting that dim, you can't tell the difference between those colors at all
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:27.80,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,True
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:30.10,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,Mine's red, so that's why it might be easier to tell
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:31.30,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Oh, it shows up really clearly
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:32.10,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it shows up clearly
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:37.00,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,But in that darkness, Kanon, Kinako, and Chisato look like the same color
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:39.60,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Yeah they all look the same
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:41.50,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's just that, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:45.80,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,Maybe we were lucky and there were not too many similar ones
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:47.40,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Huh, what about Natsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:51.00,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,But red and pink are pretty different.\NPink is lighter, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.60,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.60,0:08:54.60,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Okay, last prompt
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:56.60,Shiki,,0,0,0,,Let's do our last one
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:04.20,Shiki,,0,0,0,,"Something you did especially to prepare for this live"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:06.30,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,"Special"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.20,0:09:08.00,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,Something you did specially...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:10.00,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Something special you did?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:13.80,Shiki,,0,0,0,,I didn't even cut my hair, so I got nothing "special"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:16.80,Shiki,,0,0,0,,Didn't cut it. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:18.80,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,You said you were gonna cut it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:20.80,Shiki,,0,0,0,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:20.80,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:22.80,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Huh? You two are so close
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:28.50,Shiki,,0,0,0,,Ever since I said I'd cut it, I still haven't
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:31.40,Shiki,,0,0,0,,Still haven't been able to set a date, so I 'm still "planning to"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:34.00,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Right. Wasn't that a while ago when you said it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:36.50,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,Huh, so you {\i1}want{\i0} to cut it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:38.00,Shiki,,0,0,0,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:40.70,Shiki,,0,0,0,,I want to, but the timing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:45.20,Shiki,,0,0,0,,I'm very professional, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:53.73,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs40\pos(957.333,881.666)}Liella! Roundtable Memo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:53.73,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1016.333)\fnArial\fs40}Professionalism (high)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.20,0:09:47.20,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}Not many say that about themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:49.00,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}Probably nobody
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:53.20,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}If I cut it on some random ordinary day, it might feel different, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:53.50,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,616.333)}"Random ordinary days," huh
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:54.60,Shiki,,0,0,0,,Like, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:55.90,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,It's better if it's for something
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:10:00.00,Shiki,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like if there's an event or something, it feels right to cut it then
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:02.70,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,Yeah, at this point, yeah (like showing your milestone)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:07.20,Shiki,,0,0,0,,Then later, when you see it in photos, you're like, "Ah!"\NOtherwise, it won't feel the same
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.20,0:10:10.10,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,True, I also think about the timing a lot too
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:14.20,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,But you know, when I am gonna be out in public, I do care about that timing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.00,0:10:21.50,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,But when it comes to cutting my hair, once I feel like it, I'll immediately go the next day
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:23.70,Shiki,,0,0,0,,Ah but but but I'm the same type, the same
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:25.70,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Just go! If you've decided
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:25.70,Shiki,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:29.90,Shiki,,0,0,0,,I've got a hairstylist who always does my hair,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:32.80,Shiki,,0,0,0,,and they're like, "You absolutely should not cut it"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:32.80,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:46.30,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs40\pos(957.333,881.666)}Liella! Roundtable Memo
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:46.30,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1016.333)\fnArial\fs55}Her hairstylist strongly refuses
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:36.00,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}Then you're done for
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:38.80,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,693.666)}It's gotten so long, though, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:38.30,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}They're seriously like, "Don't cut it"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:40.30,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}"Don't you dare cut it!!!" they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:44.20,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}Hold on, you {\i1}are{\i0} a hairstylist, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:47.80,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,By the way, they said that to me too
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:50.10,Shiki,,0,0,0,,They do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:52.10,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,I want to go short
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.10,0:10:53.60,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,I really want to cut it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:56.43,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}And they're like, "Nah, don't do it~"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.43,0:11:04.30,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs40\pos(957.333,881.666)}Liella! Roundtable Memo
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.43,0:11:04.30,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1016.333)\fnArial\fs50}"Don't do it~"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.43,0:10:58.43,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}While touching my hair
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.10,0:10:59.80,Shiki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,688.333)}I get it, they also said it to me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.50,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}"Don't do it~" they said
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:07.40,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,I guess longer hair just has that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:11.20,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,"shine" to it, a kind of lovely and beauty, too
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:13.30,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,They probably already like, admiring it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:17.80,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,They love it so much to let you cut it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:20.30,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Still, if you ever feel like it, you could just try doing it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:22.80,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,Might change your mood, too
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:25.00,Shiki,,0,0,0,,True, when you get that sudden urge
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnＭＳ Ｐゴシック\fs45\pos(1696,1021.666)}"Any routine,\Nor something you\Nalways do\Nbefore live?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.60,0:11:32.30,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,{\pos(888,1035)}Do you have any routines, or anything you always do before live?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:34.80,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(828,1035)}So not just this time, but in general, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:36.16,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,I don't have one
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:40.40,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}Hey, that was fast
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:42.40,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}You just read it (already answer it)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:43.40,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,696.333)}I'm just saying, lately, I don't have one
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:48.60,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Every time? I always fix my bangs. Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:50.50,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,Ah right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:54.30,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,At the very start of the live, your bangs are always perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:58.50,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Especially lately. They have grown a bit, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:03.60,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Just trimming it around here makes me feel focused
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:05.50,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,This is my "switch"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:19.23,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs40\pos(957.333,881.666)}Liella! Roundtable Memo
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:19.23,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1016.333)\fnArial\fs55}ON-bangs > Nako Switch
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:09.30,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}Of course there have been live where my bangs is not perfectly on-point
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:11.30,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}but, as we done more lives
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:19.10,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}It makes my everyday life easier, but on stage, my view feels clearer somehow
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.10,0:12:21.20,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,But it's probably not a huge difference, though
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:20.70,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,It's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:22.20,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,It suits you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:24.20,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Thank you. That makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:26.40,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,What about you, Wakana?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:27.40,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,ROUTINE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:31.20,Shiki,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm not really good at doing the same thing every single time--like routinely
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:36.43,Shiki,,0,0,0,,Yeah… I can’t do the same thing every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:42.90,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs40\pos(957.333,881.666)}Liella! Roundtable Memo
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:42.90,Wien,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1016.333)\fnArial\fs55}Every day is a bit much…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:37.50,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}Every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:39.50,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}Every day, huh
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:41.50,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}That's a bit much
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:44.30,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,776.333)}But you know how people often say,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.30,0:12:49.50,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,“Before every live, I always do this,” right? A lot of people have things like that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:53.30,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,I used to think maybe it's better if I had one too,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:55.50,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,but after thinking about it a lot…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:13:00.10,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,I realized I’m better off not deciding one
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.10,0:13:03.60,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,It feels more natural to just go with the flow in that moment
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:06.10,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,In the end, I didn’t have one
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:08.10,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,But, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:10.40,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,It’s not like it’s “bad” that I don’t have one
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:15.60,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,It’s more like, “Yeah, this works for me.” For my own self
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:17.90,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,If that works for you, then that’s fine
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:22.80,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Also, if I decided “I have to do this,” and then I couldn’t do it, I will be in total panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:25.60,Chisato - font,,0,0,0,,Like it will throw my rhythm off
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:26.70,Shiki,,0,0,0,,I totally get that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:29.30,Mei - White,,0,0,0,,But I think it's totally fine if someone does have one
